  DIETARY REQUIREMENTS

  8OZ POST-COOK PROTEIN / 1 CUP STARCH / 1 CUP VEGETABLES
  2  WHOLE 30 MEAL  (on site kitchen to produce)
    3c mixed greens + cucumber, 1/2c cooked lentils, 1T olive oil + vinegar, 1/2 avocado, 4oz grilled salmon | sent HOT

  1  SPECIALTY MEAL  Dino Ebel – Low Sodium, no red meat, dairy-free
    plain unseasoned chicken or fish | server to place in togo box at 10:45 marked Dino

  1  CONCIERGE - JAPANESE MEALS  delivered at 10:45am by ABRAHAM

